data.description: You will fall in love with this large multi level home that has been fully remodeled and renovated, that happens to be located within the highly desired and sought after Stonecrest subdivision. Once you enter into this 4,460sq ft fully move in ready home you will notice that it has all of the finishing touches and cosmetic updates that it should be featured on hdtv. This large 5 bedroom 2.5 bath home sits on a large corner lot that happens to be just over 1/2 acre, giving you plenty of outdoor space for entertaining plus still having room for the children and your pets room to play. You will fine this home has large luxury vinyl plank flooring that is water proofed and scratch resistant, hardwoods , custom painted cabinets, granite countertops, glass backsplash, built in double ovens , see through double sided fireplace from the rec room into the large family room, Vaulted ceilings , beautiful lighting throughout the home. The 4th and 5th bedrooms are on their very own floors. The 5th bedroom even has its own entrance to the backyard and is currently being used as the kids game room/ guest room but it can easily be used as an office. Plus you will fine the upstairs bathroom also has been updated and it also has a jetted tub. There is so much more that you just have to see for yourself.
